The Arduino supports the coding languages C and C++.

To get started on some simple projects with the Arduino itself, check out this link: https://www.arduino.cc/en/Tutorial/HomePage?from=Main.Tutorials

To get started with the Muscle Spiker Shield, check out the "MuscleSpikerShieldDefaultCode" file.

For intermediate neural-engineering centered projects (you need the Muscle Spiker Shield), check out this link, under Experiments: https://backyardbrains.com/products/musclespikershield

